31#include "config.h"
32
33#if HAVE_FLOAT_H
34#include <float.h> /* for DBL_MAX */
35#endif
36
37#include "gmp.h"
38#include "gmp-impl.h"
39
40int
41mpf_cmp_d (mpf_srcptr f, double d)
42{
43 mp_limb_t darray[LIMBS_PER_DOUBLE];
44 mpf_t df;
45
46 /* d=NaN has no sensible return value, so raise an exception.
47 d=Inf or -Inf is always bigger than z. */
48 DOUBLE_NAN_INF_ACTION (d,
49 __gmp_invalid_operation (),
50 return (d < 0.0 ? 1 : -1));
51
52 if (d == 0.0)
53 return SIZ(f);
54
55 PTR(df) = darray;
56 SIZ(df) = (d >= 0.0 ? LIMBS_PER_DOUBLE : -LIMBS_PER_DOUBLE);
57 EXP(df) = __gmp_extract_double (darray, ABS(d));
58
59 return mpf_cmp (f, df);
60}
